text: The One That Got Away is a 1964 Australian television show.The One That Got Away at National Film and Sound Archive ==Plot== A family leave a teaching job and a home in the suburbs. They live in a tiny shack in the bush and the father becomes a fisherman. ==Cast== *Leonard Teale as Major Arthur Dawson *Deryck Barnes *Janette Craig *Gordon Glenwright *John Heywood *Mark McManus *June Salter *Grant Taylor *Bob McDarra ==References== ==External links== *The One That Got Away at National Film and Sound Archive Category:1964 television films Category:1964 films Category:Australian television films Category:Australian films Category:1960s Australian television plays
